onReport.t.sol
├─ when called by the price manager workflow
│  ├─ it should correctly route streams reports to the auction contract's transmit function
│  ├─ it should correctly verify streams report
│  └─ it should update asset prices
├─ when called by the auction manager workflow
│  ├─ it should correctly route the perform data to the auction contract's performUpkeep function
│  └─ it should start the auction
└─ when called by the auction bidder workflow
   ├─ it should correctly route the solution to the auction bidder's bid function
   └─ it should bid on the auction
